        Writes mac-to-mac flow on all ports that are in the path between given source and destination ports. It uses path provided by org.opendaylight.l2switch.loopremover.topology.NetworkGraphService to find a links Link between given ports. And then writes appropriate flow on each port that is covered in that path.
